Step-by-step install SSH remote di Ubuntu VirtualBox

# sudo apt-get install openssh-client (untuk sisi cleint)
# sudo apt-get install openssh-server (untuk sisi server)
# sudo cp /etc/ssh/sshd_config /etc/ssh/sshd_config.factory-defaults
# sudo chmod a-w /etc/ssh/sshd_config.factory-defaults
# sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
# sudo systemctl restart ssh
# ssh username@192.304.39.2(ip remote)

-------Membuat Shorcut Terminal SSH------
Step-by-step konfigurasi shortcut terminal
# nano ~/.ssh/config
# copy paste:
  Host ShortcutName  
  HostName IPAddress                       
  User Username
  Port PortSSH
# ssh ShortcutName


